article.headline: Lee scores 20 to lead Princeton to 70-60 victory over Brown
article.description: — Xaivian Lee's 20 points helped Princeton defeat Brown 70-60 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Lee scores 20 to lead Princeton to 70-60 victory over Brown

images.name: Princeton Holds On to Defeat Brown, 70-60  - Via Ivy League
images.caption: Xaivian Lee Scores 20 to Lead Princeton Past Brown

video.headline: Princeton Holds On to Defeat Brown, 70-60  - Via Ivy League
video.caption: Xaivian Lee Scores 20 to Lead Princeton Past Brown
video.title: Princeton Holds On to Defeat Brown, 70-60  - Via Ivy League
video.description: Xaivian Lee Scores 20 to Lead Princeton Past Brown

article.story: PROVIDENCE, R.I. -- — Xaivian Lee's 20 points helped Princeton defeat Brown 70-60 on Saturday night. Lee added five rebounds for the Tigers (16-3, 4-2 Ivy League). Caden Pierce finished with 13 points and 14 rebounds. Matt Allocco scored 13 on 5-for-9 shooting. Nana Owusu-Anane led the Bears (6-15, 2-4) with 20 points and six rebounds. Kino Lilly Jr. added 15 points and Kimo Ferrari pitched in with 11 points and six boards. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
